==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mantilla
<hw>Man*til"la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp. See
<er>Mantle</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A lady's light cloak of cape of
silk, velvet, lace, or the like.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of veil, covering the head and falling down
upon the shoulders; -- worn in Spain, Mexico, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mantineia</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Mantinea</ent>⟦br⟧
